		  plasmas.},
  oabstract =	 {We study the effect of parametric excitation of
		  quasimodes on the depletion of a lower hybrid pump
		  wave driven from a finite extent source with
		  parameters relevant to tokamak plasmas.  The set of
		  coupled nonlinear equations for the pump wave and the
